For the co-primary outcome, i.e. ∆LAZ, a linear regression model will be used to compare mean ∆LAZ across the treatment groups in surviving children. ∆LAZ will be operationalised as the difference in LAZ between the 90-day follow-up visit and LAZ at baseline. For the primary ITT analysis, LAZ outcome will only be analysed for those children with a measured outcome. The following model will be used:
